vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.universal.event

Class RegistryEvent.CreateRegistryTypesEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.universal.band_wagon.Event
      • vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.universal.event.RegistryEvent.CreateRegistryTypesEvent
  • Enclosing class:
    RegistryEvent

    public static class RegistryEvent.CreateRegistryTypesEvent
extends Event
    Called to signify the point at which all mods should create new RegistryTypes. Contains a helper method so that that creation can take place in the event, rather than from the RegistryTypes class, partly so that all of the calls are executed from the main thread, reducing the chance for synchronisation issues between threads with disparate, unsynchronised RegistryTypes later.
    Author:
    GenElectrovise
